Diminas Dagogo bụ onye nduzi ihe nkiri si Rivers State, Nigeria nke a maara nke ọma maka ejiji ya na ọrụ mmetụta pụrụ iche na ihe nkiri Nollywood. Ọ natara nhọpụta ihe nrite AMVCA abụọ maka ọrụ ya na Stigma (2013), nke gosipụtara Hilda Dokubo
Dagogo bụ onye gụrụ akwụkwọ na Mahadum Port Harcourt ma biri ugbu a na Berlin / Germany.
